{{TAGDEF|LIBXC2|[string] or [integer]}}

Description: {{TAG|LIBXC2}} specifies the correlation functional from the library of exchange-correlation functionals Libxc{{cite|marques:cpc:2012}}{{cite|lehtola:sx:2018}}{{cite|libxc}}. {{TAG|LIBXC2}} can be used only if the functional specified with {{TAG|LIBXC1}} corresponds to only exchange and not to exchange and correlation.

----
A detailed explanation of how to use {{TAG|LIBXC1}} and {{TAG|LIBXC2}} and examples can be found on the {{TAG|LIBXC1}} page.

